	   <tr><td colspan=2>Invigor just brings the yellow bar back up not needed much until you get to higher lvl's.<br><br>Spirit of Cheetah is a spell I keep up when soloing or running a zone that has some bad agro mobs. Several lvl's ago I guess about 20 lvl's now. Was running fv when that iksar necro lvl 55 or so saw me he rooted me first then feared me. so lost sow/scale of wolf good thing I had Cheetah memed and up. When fear ran out was able to cast and make it to the city safely. <br><br>I alwasy keep it up if going to travel any distance for emergencies or when soloing in case I need to zone.<br><br>Bedin Sowgood 46th Shaman on Povar<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
