	   <tr><td colspan=2>In my opinion all the races have different role playing strengths. the Troll and Ogre are good if you want a Tank that casts spells; The Barb and Iskar if you want a caster that tanks. You'll notice the Difference in a group, the Troll'Ogre tends to be a Nuke (cast dot, dd, melee) and the others a Healer (cast dot, med, heal). This is because of the inherent strengths of the race involved. There is no "best race" for shamans, only the best race for the person involved. I prefer the Barb, as I am one, because I tend to help others and try not to melee that often as there's plenty of tanks; and Iskars armor and weapons for shammies suck (in my opinion only there are others who love that, I started one but didn't care for her, but Iskar SK's rock!)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
