	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, I feel this subject is worth my attention since so many seem to be one sided. Thumbs up to Pusbag for your round about graceful attempt in claiming that ALL races have positives and negatives to them as I too support this thought. By all means, first and foremost, one should birth a character because this is what interests you and secondly on stats as in the long run, this will only become foder for the ego. Yet, since so many were willing to be one-sided on the issue, I too will take the time to support the ssscaley clan.<br><br>Yes all other Shaman get bash and are much stronger in melee stats to start off with than the Iky'sss. Although our high wisdom has something to be said of itself in the early years as well. And, if you are the melee type, by all means, go with one of these class'. Yet as for myself, being a Hillbilly, a Fato, or an Uglo simply gave no interest.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>Believe it or not, I chose this class for the shear complexity of it. Yes, Ogre and Troll are hated, but niether have the hatred presented upon them like the Iksar. This in my many years of life has become as much joy with regards to traveling as I was hoping it to be, excluding Velious which is a whole new world, literally. There is nothing better than to be chased by a swarm of racist guards who shout at me how I have ruined my home and they will NOT have me ruin theirs. As if any of these foolish guards have A) even been to Kunark and B) anywhere near any entrance much less inside my beautiful and peaceful home.<br><br>We, like all races, are just as brotherly within our own race and I would even be willing to go so far as to say the most brotherly of races considering we all know the trials and tribulations of traveling. I on a number of occasions have turned many a paleskin away who has approached me in the most rudest of manners demanding a SoW only to freely throw one on a passing brethren. I also get much joy in explaining to all the racist beggars that unless you are willing to shout "I LOVE CAZIC-THULE", do not expect to receive a SoW. (Please give me props for my wonderful sense of RP Pusbag:))<br><br>More importantly, I am a Shaman, a spiritualist. And, as spiritualist am a firm believer that a good deed done produces good karma in the long run, and have in my years toned down my hatred toward the racist world realizing that they are merely weak in mind and spirit and that a true follower of the spirit should be willing to show the unholy the path of truth...that being that Iksar rule!    <br>&nbsp;<br>Xtreem Victorinox<br>Iksar Shaman<br>Tempestas Equus<br>Arbites Telepathica<br>Solusek Ro<br></td></tr>
