	   <tr><td colspan=2>Personally I'm playing an Ogre Shammie and i have no doubt I made the right decision. I feel that their STA is high enough to make for the extra HP trolls get during a battle from their high regen. Their Strength is unparalleled. They can not be stunned from the front which kicks butt cause then you don't get interupted casting. You get bash so you can stun other casters you fight. And you're not completely KOS everywhere.<br><br>Something else you may want to note, It's nearly impossible to raise faction with both the good races and the evil races at the same time. but by being an evil race you can generally stay so-so with the darkies and still get on the lighties good side. And i've been told that cabilis faction doesn't screw up any other faction. <br><br>IMHO Ogres are the best...but i'm SURE you'll find differing oppinions.<br><br>/em looks at Pusbag wondering how long it will take him to open that maw of his.<br>&nbsp;<br>Pilapeu Wewingtonheet<br>SilentFist Clan<br>Seventh Hammer Server</td></tr>
